    "description": "Head out to Moonlight Mountain at midnight with your glowing snowboard and snowmobile, but be careful out there... Sometimes when you hit the slopes at night, the slopes hit back. <i>GlowBoard: WinterFest </i>is a celebration of couch gaming and nostalgic snowy sillyness, including split-screen and online snowboard battles, snowmobile races and a unique puzzle arcade snow fort destruction mode. Race against other local riders or challenge AI, try and find some power-ups along the trail to make things a little more interesting. Welcome to <i>GlowBoard</i>, let's ride! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841820/extras/c1586a0e64793eaa42fa9329a4b8b4cb.avif?t=1695661058\" width=470 height=260 /></span><br><strong>Featuring Three Unique Game Modes:</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GlowBoard</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Local 4-player split-screen snowboard action *<br></li><li> Take the action online with matchmaking<br></li><li>Race or battle it out for points on the slopes<br></li><li>Several vastly nasty different trails to ride</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841820/extras/a00b5632b379b7e87656056520cf7fa9.avif?t=1695661058\" width=256 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GlowMobile </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Snowmobile combat racing!<br></li><li>Race online or against AI<br></li><li>Split-screen snowmobile madness!<br></li><li><i>King of the Hill</i> survival mode</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NightFort</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique game mode with familiar billiards-inspired rules<br></li><li>Place, angle and size snow ramps then jump off those ramps<br></li><li>Use your body to try and destroy a series of fort puzzles<br></li><li>Play your friend locally or solo puzzle challenge mode</li></ul><br><br><strong>Including...</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841820/extras/3ffa59e29ce433c004cd0293a751dd33.avif?t=1695661058\" width=256 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Races</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pickup powerups galore! Use them to conquer the slopes. (Optionally)<br></li><li>Bombs, bananas, lightning, and more! Including the dreaded yellow snowballs<br></li><li>Solo adventures or AI to race against (GlowBoard or GlowMobile)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841820/extras/67064f8f45af4e0f582cacf30b0bc54d.avif?t=1695661058\" width=256 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lodge</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Warm &amp; cozy, immersive &amp; interactive lodge menu as home base<br></li><li>Head back to the lodge to check out your new unlocks and customize your ride<br></li><li>Choose from a hundred unlockable riders each with a variety of skin and outfit colors, dozens of hats, tons of snowboard designs and snowmobile colors</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841820/extras/3c0f2af21ae698d15585d9efa5c7b5df.avif?t=1695661058\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br><br>Plus everything is glowing and the game takes place at night, did I forget to mention that? The mountain is more fun at night!<br><br>*Multiplayer local split-screen requires multiple controllers, this game was designed with controllers in mind so plug one in for the best experience<br><br><i>Developed with love by an independent solo developer in Florida who misses the snow.</i>",
